---

## Blocking vs non-blocking

Blocking:

```text
failed ruff
failed pytest
failed frontend tests
failed frontend build
failed safety-scan
tracked .env
tracked secrets
tracked local-only codex-runs
live trading enabled
port 8000 introduced in runtime/source files
Docker/compose failure if Docker validation is required for the release
```

Non-blocking when summaries pass:

```text
passlib crypt deprecation warning from dependency
React act(...) warnings in existing tests
React Router future flag warnings
intentional ErrorBoundary test Error: fail
Vite chunk-size warning
Docker skipped because unavailable
```

---

## Commit

If the report is written into docs, commit it:

```bash
git add docs

git commit -m "phase35.6: add final release handoff report"
```

If no files changed, do not create an empty commit. Return the report only.
